issue.title: Replace OID/NID spreadsheet reference with link to current markdown file
issue.body: As per discussion in https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/openssl/pull/311 [the reference to the ID spreadsheet](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/oqs-demos/blob/a0e0ba96691acea6f8afa21d6d0cc6f147103eae/nginx/fulltest/index-template#L36) is stale and needs to be replaced once https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/openssl/pull/311 or https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/openssl/pull/313 have landed.

issue.title: Create ARM64 Ubuntu image
issue.body: In support of https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/issues/1007 . Maybe not go as far as creating multi-platform image but just one that can be properly referenced in a native machine runner test.
